  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0644da355aa0fa14983545f2d60c0c31, type: 3}
  m_Name: SpecialPerson
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  questionText: You're pretty... special, huh? Different from other people?
  traitsRevealed:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 65b960290032cc048a02be92fc50ee7c, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 138db3ffc7861704d8012aa6e86b9a09, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: dfa441996a5f7f54398da0de2558ff37, type: 2}
  defaultReply: Well, all of us our different in our own ways.
  replyKey:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 65b960290032cc048a02be92fc50ee7c, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 138db3ffc7861704d8012aa6e86b9a09, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: dfa441996a5f7f54398da0de2558ff37, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 098e1c4a655ee734f8a6bffc6cf738ce, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0fd171517e1147a4398fc997692f8f0e, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: a5e031b4b8ad96643858c00f5b5b1358, type: 2}
  replyText:
  - Oh, so you can see that, huh...? You can see the darkness within me?
  - What, is it because I talk a lot? My bad, my bad, but I can't really control
    it! I mean, I can't really explain what I mean in so little words. Every word
    I say is mandatory!
  - Oh, so you're saying I smell, huh? Everyone keeps saying that, but I took my
    deoderant! So you're wrong.
  - I mean yeah, I got some very different interests than your average person...
  - What? You talking about my acting style?
  - I mean, if you're talking about my outgoingness, sure.
